    function search() {
        entry = document.getElementById('entry').value;
        if (entry.length <= 2) { return 0; }
        found = false;
        
        document.getElementById('results').innerHTML = '<ul >';
        for (i = 0; i < index.length; i++) {
            for (j = 0; j < index[i][3].length; j++) {
                if (index[i][3][j].toLowerCase().indexOf(entry.toLowerCase()) == 0) {
                    document.getElementById('results').innerHTML += '    <li>Encontrado <i>' + index[i][3][j] + '</i> en <a href="' + index[i][1] + '/' + index[i][2] + '.html">' + index[i][0] + '</a></li>';
                    found = true;
                }
            }
        }
        document.getElementById('results').innerHTML += '</ul >';
        if (!found) {
            document.getElementById('results').innerHTML = 'Sin resultados'; 
        }
    }
